641
00:46:53.758 --> 00:46:54.801
Pai?

642
00:48:31.314 --> 00:48:32.524
Sabe...

643
00:48:33.859 --> 00:48:34.943
...Igby...

644
00:48:36.194 --> 00:48:38.321
...sinto uma...

645
00:48:38.530 --> 00:48:39.823
...grande...

646
00:48:42.450 --> 00:48:43.660
...pressão...

647
00:48:45.537 --> 00:48:47.080
...sobre mim.

648
00:48:48.999 --> 00:48:53.378
